quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33366,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/07\/fasting-9th-10th-muharram\/","url_meta":{"origin":28113,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ashura: Fasting 9th and 10th of Muharram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered fasting on the day of 'Ashura, the tenth of al-Muharram. Imam al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cIt is reported from Ibn Abbas that he said to fast on the ninth and tenth of the month and to do so\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1641,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/27\/best-after-ramadan-muharram\/","url_meta":{"origin":28113,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Best fast after Ramadan is Muharram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best prayer after the prescribed prayers is a prayer offered in the middle of the night. The best fast after the month of Ramadan is fasting in the month of Allah, al-Muharram.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/cat